metadata.description: This plain-format SVG comes ready to use with commercial and consumer plotter/cutting machines. You may make stickers, mugs, T-shirts, and more. Though the vector can be scaled to any size, it is pre-sized for cutting heat-transfer vinyl to be applied to baseball caps and trucker hats. [Click here](https://arweave.net/V7H_Mzu7n8R_PnIveQpGb7iAS_yV9UOV0VA1QgNKBMY) to download the SVG and to review the licenses for personal (CC BY-NC-SA) and commercial (Modified NFTL 1.0) use. Owners of this NFT enjoy all the privileges of the commercial use license.
